{"tid":173220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90 00後青年生涯規劃!","createTime":"2017-03-26T06:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T06:53:17.000Z","uid":19707,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd55d37547788f2c1d4cef30469e4cbbf376752","tid":173220,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"一出生<br />\n就要玩啲咩playgroup<br />\n話咩促進腦部發展<br />\n去到幼稚園,<br />\n又話要prep 面試<br />\n仲有個Pre-school Interview Training Class<br />\n<a href=\"http://youngtalents.com.hk/ENGnew.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoungtalents.com.hk%2FENGnew.htm&d=Iox0GB6uY5Umm6P4cmuVh26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ce9571c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://youngtalents.com.hk/ENGnew.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n去到小學,<br />\n又tsa又要準備中學面試<br />\n功課又出奇地多,又難<br />\n仲要一個星期幾個興趣班一齊上<br />\n何解?要入st.paul co-ed呀嗎<br />\n要入DBS DGS 呀嗎<br />\n可以同人講,<br />\n哇,我個女入咗DGS呀!<br />\n<br />\n但,很遺憾地,<br />\n人地通常係一條龍的<br />\n如果你好彩入到<br />\n入面大多數都係上流人士子女,<br />\n排斥你,你又受唔受得起?<br />\n同埋入面唔包生仔的,<br />\n如果你認為入DGS=人生成功<br />\n那只能說你是too simple too naive,<br />\n<br />\n無得入dgs,入咗間band 2 學校<br />\n但band 2 學校好多時教學質素參差,<br />\n做窮人,無得送去英國讀boarding school<br />\n唯有考DSE<br />\nDSE好講運的,都好講家庭環境<br />\n任你校內成績如何,<br />\n一唔覺意中文2咗就byebye.<br />\n如果屋企好嘈,你又無房<br />\n你覺得你DSE成績會有幾高?<br />\n<br />\n想脫貧想改變<br />\n唯有讀醫讀專業科<br />\n醫科,admission score 極高<br />\n法律,考唔到PCLL就玩完<br />\nengine,各大院校出極多fresh grad<br />\n鑑於香港各大院校爛grade<br />\n唔係cv 極出色 都無可能入mtr,clp等local 大公司<br />\n政府?fresh grad 搶住入,你真係入到?<br />\n<br />\n出來打工,無經驗通常會俾HR壓價,<br />\n香港的職場文化是 唯老闆獨尊<br />\n敢同老闆頂撞,就會俾佢玩死.<br />\n見做得唔開心,唯有辭職<br />\n想再做,HR問你,<br />\n何解有幾個月vacant period?<br />\n是不是你懶唔搵工?<br />\n到時候你只有無言以對.<br />\n<br />\n好啦,有女朋友了(A0例外)<br />\n成家立室了<br />\n照計都要有個私人空間<br />\n公屋?排番十幾年都未到你<br />\n居屋?抽到先算<br />\n私樓?市區要千零萬,合埋人工得四萬,買唔起,<br />\n屯天元?出去市區打工來回都三個鐘<br />\n<br />\n之但係,人始終都要住<br />\n所以無錢的年輕人就月供1xxxx供30年屯天元了.<br />\n人工無加,只能住死一世屯天元了.<br />\n香港年輕人的未來就好像是一潭死水一樣,亳無生氣.<br />\n<br />\n香港自被中國接管以後<br />\n其實已經死咗了<br />\n年輕人與其活著受氣<br />\n倒不如自殺算.<br />\n<br />\n自殺危機處理中心:<br />\n地址：九龍白田邨瑞田樓3樓1室<br />\n電話：2341 7227 傳真：2341 7007<br />\n電郵：alive@sbhk.org.hk"},{"pid":"e00f3f104139057f5dbac3313abe4b80517a3ed0","tid":173220,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7143fc29dbbe584791d6b532b12f9f9e905fa243","tid":173220,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce4e7301c7e615393682375d5becc2707de18a0","tid":173220,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">會活動的奴役工具</span>"},{"pid":"8fbcf9861a7f9892e2246c149fcd01d759218b78","tid":173220,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj